De_stronghold

A team of terrorists are infiltrating an underground bunker, which houses important military information and supplies. 

As terrorists your objective is to destroy the generators, which will cut off the facility's power supply. Alternatively, blow up the data servers and land a crippling blow on the military's intelligence operations. 

As counter-terrorists your objective is to stop the terrorists accomplishing their objective at all costs.

Map made by Ares, with credit to Valve for the de_prodigy map.
